cs.NI, cs.MM, cs.IT, cs.CR, cs.SY

The paper discusses the increase in mobile traffic due to multimedia content and proposes a cell association algorithm to resolve the nomadic heavy user problem. This topic is closely related to network infrastructure (cs.NI), multimedia (cs.MM), information theory (cs.IT), cryptography and security (cs.CR), and systems and control (cs.SY). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
